      <div class="subfield"><strong>$i - Method of action</strong> <div class="description">Means or technique by which an action was performed.</div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Examples of means include: by mail, in person, by phone for reference services.
                                 Examples of technique include: scrap, incinerate, shred for disposition.
            </div>
