      <div class="subfield"><strong>$l - Status</strong> <div class="description">Condition or state of the described materials</div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Condition is sometimes but not always resulting from an action (e.g., physical
                                 condition, insurance value, or description status). For preservation activities,
                                 this subfield may contain information about the condition of the item when the
                                 action is, for example, <em>condition reviewed</em>. This subfield may also
                                 contain information about the status of the item that caused preservation to be
                                 rejected (e.g., action is <em>preservation rejected</em>) or information about the
                                 disposition of the original item (e.g., action is <em>reformatted</em>).
            </div>
